{"id": 2012, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得，什么样的向导可以给你的旅行加分？", "description": "强制购物拿提成在哪儿都招人烦，但向导还有很多方式得到好评啊。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 7389, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171114151432LFGl2Ua6zVYdf7Zw.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-15T17:00:44Z", "questions": [{"id": 3281, "title": "你觉得，什么样的向导可以给你的旅行加分？", "content": "你觉得，什么样的向导可以给你的旅行加分？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 248912, "content": "不背导游词，不讲瞎编帝王传说的导游，真正介绍当地风貌和生活", "image": "img/option/option/2017111515581345aQAtidwuVnxBcG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248913, "content": "博物馆安静的讲解员，看到我对一个展品感兴趣，主动告诉我它的背后故事", "image": "img/option/option/20171115160527sXOY5qVEPe9tgQy3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248914, "content": "保姆型贴心，关怀衣食住行，照顾口味和生活习惯", "image": "img/option/option/20171115160649i89oJwkUyTHLuZ1R.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248920, "content": "在当地上培训课程认识的负责而博学的老师，在上课中感受文化差异", "image": "img/option/option/201711151609531CbaGs6xVMowgZYN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248921, "content": "杜绝“强制团客型购物”，但如果能介绍正宗的本地特产也很好", "image": "img/option/option/20171115161207XEkAu07KR9YoIOUt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248922, "content": "身兼数职，讲解到位，拍照好看的包车司机，彻底不用做攻略", "image": "img/option/option/20171115161338kswj7fXPGxRiY4TI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248923, "content": "贴心民宿老板，推荐附近好吃好玩的地方，尤其是跟大众点评和攻略上不一样的那些", "image": "img/option/option/20171115161548z1Kv9g4fcTJZpNq2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248916, "content": "相比真人导游，为旅行量身定制的旅行手册和导览APP更适合我", "image": "img/option/option/20171115160759O4xDo5cZgtGPj803.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}